{"uid":"2eb7c6415d41dac2","name":"test_voice_selection_from_chat","fullName":"tests.ui.voice.test_voice_configuration.TestVoiceConfiguration#test_voice_selection_from_chat","historyId":"bcdcd66481fb57cc341a06abead3dad2","time":{"start":1782482241144,"stop":1782482260554,"duration":19410},"description":"TC1: Voice Selection via TTS Controls in Chat.\n        TC-1918, TC-1915\n        Steps:\n            1. Navigate to Chat, send a message, wait for AI response\n            2. Click 'Read out' (speaker) icon on AI response\n            3. Click gear/settings icon in TTS control bar\n            4. Inspect all dialog elements (Voice, Speed, Volume, Cancel, Apply)\n            5. Click Voice dropdown - verify non-empty list\n            6. Select a voice different from current\n            7. Click Apply - dialog closes, voice saved\n            8. Re-open Voice Settings - verify voice persisted\n            9. Change voice again, click Cancel - verify reverts to applied voice\n        ","descriptionHtml":"<p>TC1: Voice Selection via TTS Controls in Chat.<br />\nTC-1918, TC-1915<br />\nSteps:<br />\n1. Navigate to Chat, send a message, wait for AI response<br />\n2. Click 'Read out' (speaker) icon on AI response<br />\n3. Click gear/settings icon in TTS control bar<br />\n4. Inspect all dialog elements (Voice, Speed, Volume, Cancel, Apply)<br />\n5. Click Voice dropdown - verify non-empty list<br />\n6. Select a voice different from current<br />\n7. Click Apply - dialog closes, voice saved<br />\n8. Re-open Voice Settings - verify voice persisted<br />\n9. Change voice again, click Cancel - verify reverts to applied voice</p>\n","status":"passed","flaky":false,"newFailed":false,"newBroken":false,"newPassed":false,"retriesCount":0,"retriesStatusChange":false,"beforeStages":[{"name":"pytestconfig","time":{"start":1782480503270,"stop":1782480503270,"duration":0},"status":"passed","steps":[],"attachments":[],"parameters":[],"shouldDisplayMessage":false,"stepsCount":0,"atta